<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 20:07:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“伊斯兰国向俄罗斯普京发出新的威胁”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/isis-issues-fresh-threat-to-putin-russia/articleshow/108793825.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108793825.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;针对俄罗斯的新威胁以伊斯兰国（IS）海报的形式出现在社交媒体上。此前不久，该组织声称对莫斯科音乐中心的袭击事件负责。这张海报出自“呼罗珊”组织的宣传网络 Al Azaim，海报上有一个蒙面人物拿着一把刀，上面写着针对俄罗斯和普京的威胁信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 13:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/isis-issues-fresh-threat-to-putin-russia/articleshow/108793825.cms</guid></item><item><title>《生活大爆炸》的起源：揭开真实的故事</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/the-origin-of-big-bang-unraveling-the-true-story/articleshow/108793660.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108793660.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 12:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/the-origin-of-big-bang-unraveling-the-true-story/articleshow/108793660.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国法院推迟对阿桑奇最后一搏引渡上诉的裁决</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-court-orders-to-delay-extradition-of-wikileaks-founder-julian-assange-to-the-us-on-espionage-charges/articleshow/108791249.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108791249.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国高等法院周二判定维基解密创始人朱利安·阿桑奇取得了部分胜利，称他不能因间谍罪立即被引渡到美国，并且可以对此提出上诉。高等法院的两名法官表示，除非美国当局提供额外保证，否则他们将允许朱利安阿桑奇提起新的上诉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 11:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-court-orders-to-delay-extradition-of-wikileaks-founder-julian-assange-to-the-us-on-espionage-charges/articleshow/108791249.cms</guid></item><item><title>香港取消提前释放国家安全罪犯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hong-kong-scraps-early-release-for-national-security-convicts/articleshow/108778228.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108778228.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;香港领导人周二宣布，根据香港当局新实施的一项法律，因国家安全罪名被定罪的个人将不再有资格因表现良好而提前释放。做出这一决定之前，当地媒体报道称，2021 年因“煽动分裂国家罪”被判有罪的民主活动人士马俊文预计将于周一获释，但已被拘留。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 05:10:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hong-kong-scraps-early-release-for-national-security-convicts/articleshow/108778228.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾在清晨导弹演习中测试防空系统</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-tests-air-defences-in-early-morning-missile-drills/articleshow/108777410.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108777410.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 04:38:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-tests-air-defences-in-early-morning-missile-drills/articleshow/108777410.cms</guid></item><item><title>纽约警察局官员在皇后区交通堵塞期间被杀</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nypd-officer-killed-during-queens-traffic-stop/articleshow/108776300.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108776300.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一晚上，皇后区发生了一起悲惨事件，31 岁的纽约市警察局警官乔纳森·迪勒 (Jonathan Diller) 在一次例行交通检查中被嫌疑人盖伊·里维拉 (Guy Rivera) 腹部开枪打死。官员称其为“毫无意义的暴力行为”。迪勒的妻子和一岁的儿子幸存，他在试图将里维拉从车上救出来时被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:55:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nypd-officer-killed-during-queens-traffic-stop/articleshow/108776300.cms</guid></item><item><title>凯特·米德尔顿 (Kate Middleton) 确诊后，50 岁以下人群癌症发病率上升引发警惕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/alarm-over-rising-cancer-rates-among-under-50s-following-kate-middletons-diagnosis/articleshow/108776191.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108776191.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于凯特·米德尔顿 (Kate Middleton) 意外被诊断出癌症，50 岁以下人群中癌症患病率不断上升，引发了全球健康担忧。科学家们正在紧急调查潜在原因，包括环境因素、生活方式选择和遗传倾向。像米德尔顿这样备受瞩目的病例凸显了早期发现和治疗的必要性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/alarm-over-rising-cancer-rates-among-under-50s-following-kate-middletons-diagnosis/articleshow/108776191.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国着眼台湾和印度推出新型攻击直升机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-z-21-helicopter-pla-china-attack-helicopter-china-and-taiwan/articleshow/108776110.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108776110.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-z-21-helicopter-pla-china-attack-helicopter-china-and-taiwan/articleshow/108776110.cms</guid></item><item><title>“困惑、失望”：以色列决定取消代表团访问后美国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/perplexed-disappointed-us-after-israels-decision-to-cancel-delegation-visit/articleshow/108775193.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108775193.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:21:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/perplexed-disappointed-us-after-israels-decision-to-cancel-delegation-visit/articleshow/108775193.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国青少年在警局用警枪开枪自杀</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-teen-fatally-shoots-self-with-officers-gun-at-sheriff-station/articleshow/108775798.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108775798.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当局周一表示，一名十几岁的女孩在加利福尼亚州一个治安官站的大厅里用警员的枪开枪自杀。洛杉矶县治安部门表示，周日的死亡事件“不是警员参与枪击事件”，这是警官开枪射击时使用的术语。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:33:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-teen-fatally-shoots-self-with-officers-gun-at-sheriff-station/articleshow/108775798.cms</guid></item><item><title>面对调查，博尔索纳罗在匈牙利大使馆住了两晚</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/facing-probe-bolsonaro-spent-two-nights-at-hungarian-embassy/articleshow/108775363.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108775363.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴西前总统雅伊尔·博尔索纳罗的法律团队驳斥了前往匈牙利驻巴西利亚大使馆寻求庇护的说法。据《纽约时报》报道，博尔索纳罗的护照被没收，两名助手被捕，二月份他在大使馆被“接待”了两天。美国报纸发布的视频显示，博尔索纳罗于2月12日至14日在大使馆内。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/facing-probe-bolsonaro-spent-two-nights-at-hungarian-embassy/articleshow/108775363.cms</guid></item><item><title>新西兰指责中国黑客攻击议会并谴责活动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/new-zealand-accuses-china-of-hacking-parliament-condemns-activity/articleshow/108774551.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108774551.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在全球对网络间谍活动的指控之际，新西兰政府就 2021 年网络黑客事件与中国对峙。澳大利亚谴责此类活动。中国大使馆否认参与其中。与国家安全部有联系的 APT40 在网络事件中针对新西兰议会。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 02:45:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/new-zealand-accuses-china-of-hacking-parliament-condemns-activity/articleshow/108774551.cms</guid></item><item><title>英属印度青少年凶手的刑罚“过分宽大”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/unduly-lenient-sentence-of-british-indian-teens-murderer-reviewed/articleshow/108774557.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108774557.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 02:45:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/unduly-lenient-sentence-of-british-indian-teens-murderer-reviewed/articleshow/108774557.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克的星链终端落入坏人之手</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musks-starlink-terminals-are-falling-into-wrong-hands/articleshow/108774365.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108774365.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; Starlink 是 SpaceX 的一项计划，通过自 2019 年以来发射的约 5,500 颗卫星组成的网络提供宽带互联网。Starlink 目前为约 260 万客户提供服务，有望大幅提高 SpaceX 的收入。 SpaceX 最初由埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 怀着火星探索的愿景创立，现已发展成为美国政府太空计划的关键参与者和国家安全的主要贡献者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 02:35:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musks-starlink-terminals-are-falling-into-wrong-hands/articleshow/108774365.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京称激进伊斯兰分子袭击了莫斯科，但仍寻求与乌克兰有联系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-says-radical-islamists-attacked-moscow-still-seeks-ukraine-link/articleshow/108774395.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108774395.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯当局周一展示了四名男子被指控对音乐厅实施袭击的录像，审讯显示他们来自塔吉克斯坦。根据莫斯科法院服务 Telegram 频道的公告，在该组织中，有两人承认参与了此次袭击。这四人已被拘留至5月22日。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 02:36:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-says-radical-islamists-attacked-moscow-still-seeks-ukraine-link/articleshow/108774395.cms</guid></item><item><title>联邦突击搜查以肖恩·“吹牛老爹”·库姆斯的住宅为目标，开展性交易调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/federal-raids-target-sean-diddy-combs-homes-in-sex-trafficking-investigation/articleshow/108774249.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108774249.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;著名嘻哈大亨肖恩·“迪迪”·库姆斯在洛杉矶和迈阿密的家因性交易和性侵犯指控而遭到国土安全调查人员的突击搜查。虽然官员们没有透露具体细节，但这些行动是在一系列指控库姆斯不当行为的诉讼之后进行的，其中包括指控前女友卡西进行性交易。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 02:30:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/federal-raids-target-sean-diddy-combs-homes-in-sex-trafficking-investigation/articleshow/108774249.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其官员称，莫斯科袭击者短暂进入土耳其是为了更新俄罗斯居留许可</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/moscow-attackers-briefly-entered-turkey-to-renew-russian-residence-permits-turkish-official-says/articleshow/108774002.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108774002.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 02:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/moscow-attackers-briefly-entered-turkey-to-renew-russian-residence-permits-turkish-official-says/articleshow/108774002.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的净资产达到 65 亿美元，成为世界 500 名最富有的人之一</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-net-worth-hits-6-5-billion-making-him-one-of-worlds-500-richest-people/articleshow/108773598.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773598.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;州上诉法院将特朗普在纽约欺诈诉讼中必须缴纳的保证金从 5 亿多美元大幅减少至 1.75 亿美元。与此同时，特朗普媒体与科技集团完成了一项持续 29 个月的合并，导致特朗普拥有目前价值为数十亿。因此，特朗普的净资产飙升超过40亿美元，使他首次跻身彭博亿万富翁指数前500名。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 01:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-net-worth-hits-6-5-billion-making-him-one-of-worlds-500-richest-people/articleshow/108773598.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日利亚 130 多名被绑架学童在被囚禁数周后正在返回家园</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-130-abducted-schoolchildren-in-nigeria-are-returning-home-after-weeks-in-captivity/articleshow/108773498.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773498.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 3月7日，这些孩子在偏远的卡杜纳州库里加镇的学校被骑摩托车的枪手劫持，引发了广泛的营救行动。他们周日在邻近扎姆法拉州以北约 200 公里（超过 120 英里）的森林中被军方救出，不过当局没有提供救援细节，也没有透露是否有绑架嫌疑人被捕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 00:20:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-130-abducted-schoolchildren-in-nigeria-are-returning-home-after-weeks-in-captivity/articleshow/108773498.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯告诉调解人它将坚持停火的最初立场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-tells-mediators-it-will-stick-to-original-position-on-ceasefire/articleshow/108773452.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773452.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 00:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-tells-mediators-it-will-stick-to-original-position-on-ceasefire/articleshow/108773452.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>